<br />\n免費嘅原來係因為要逼你一定要隔離醫治唔可以周圍走，唔係香港咁中門大開人道主義歡迎光臨免費招待。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安倍1月27日宣佈，將把新型冠狀病毒肺炎納入日本《感染症法》裡面的「指定感染症」。這意味著，無論患者屬於哪個國家，醫療費用都將由日本來承擔。日方由此可以從法律上強制患者入院治療，並限制其行為。"},{"pid":"0385bf8622ee9677ce8befb7d352c5ef79c8dc46","tid":1846193,"uid":281232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦，唔封關累撚死香港人依啲係乜嘢道德呀？殺人兇手"},{"pid":"3fb76dc7cb1e4c8af2b3ab66ca2ecb6134f5329d","tid":1846193,"uid":58164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:51:55.000Z","msg":"呢單野真係愈黎愈有陰謀"},{"pid":"58c4143293eb7822931360be9936f86a9d70a3db","tid":1846193,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846888</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ba2cc573bcd70f076bfcbc022d27550493160e","tid":1846193,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:36:26.000Z","msg":"It's not right!<br />\n<br />\nIf his wife is very sick, why does he need to take care of wifes of others first? Will he do it?"},{"pid":"d873eb944a6971c1a8fe107b161ee30641b61319","tid":1846193,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"Social responsibility is greater than moral responsibility.<br />\n<br />\nThey need to be accountable to HK Citizen FIRST."}]}